com.skyisland.questmanager.loot.dynamic

Class DynamicLoot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skyisland.questmanager.loot.Loot
      • com.skyisland.questmanager.loot.dynamic.DynamicLoot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable

    public class DynamicLoot
extends Loot
    Loot class which holds a dynamic item rather than a static one. In other words, specifics about the item are generated fresh each time (like enchantments, name, etc)

      • registerGenerator

        public static void registerGenerator(java.lang.String configkey,
                                     DynamicGenerator generator)
        Adds the provided generator to the table of available generators, used when pieces of loot attempt to specify what method of selecting various attributes. This method is intended to allow plugins to add their own generators and have the loot use it. If you are writing a plugin for QM, you are encouraged to use this method.
        Parameters:
        configkey - The key specified in the loot's config
        generator - The generator to use when given the above key
